data.description: This beautiful two-story, three bedroom home nestled inside of the popular Stoney Creek subdivision awaits you.  The home has beautiful engineered wood floors on the main level, a large great room with gas fireplace, oversized en suite, lots of closet space, and a spacious loft which can be used as a 4th bedroom, home office, playroom for the kids, weightroom, family room or whatever your heart desires.  So many options and potential here.  The furnace is only two months old and the water heater is less than five years old.  Both the kitchen and garage door are equipped with smart home technology.  All appliances stay including the refrigerator.  This home won't last long.  Call now to see it for yourself in person!
